m\": 389, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"their country's flag\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Billions of spectators will tune in from different parts of the globe to watch their respective nations taking centre stage at the grand opening ceremony in the French capital, but all eyes will be on Team Mongolia.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9993407327485858, \"rank\": 0.0006580356627797641, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Billions\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"different parts\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective nations\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"centre stage\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the grand opening ceremony\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"all eyes\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Mongolia's new uniform designed for the opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics has set a new benchmark in simple yet majestic fashion.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"a new benchmark\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"simple yet majestic fashion\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Designed by the extremely talented designer sisters Michel and Amazonka, these outfits blends Mongolia's rich culture with modern aesthetics, demonstrating how minimalistic fashion can capture everyone's imagination.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"score\": 0.9999999991478035, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazonka\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazonka\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the extremely talented designer sisters\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"Michel\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"modern aesthetics\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"how minimalistic fashion\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone's imagination\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interestingly, it wasn't their first attempt.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their first attempt\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You see, creating magic takes time!\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"magic\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The talented sisters had previously designed Team Mongolia's uniforms in the previous two editions -2020 Tokyo Olympicsand 2022 Beijing Winter Games, but those attires did not make such noise.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999449756, \"rank\": 5.380437480892058e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The talented sisters\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous two editions\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"those attires\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"such noise\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, they were not even supposed to design the uniforms.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the uniforms\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Mongolian National Olympic Committee (MNOC) had given the contract to another company.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mongolian National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_National_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"MNOC\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"the contract\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"another company\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, that company backed off from the deal for some reason in February, leaving the governing body in a spot of bother.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that company\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"the deal\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"some reason\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"the governing body\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"bother\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since Michel & Amazonka had already delivered similar projects in the past, the MNOC reached out to them, offering only three months to conceptualise and design the uniform.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Michel\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"Amazonka\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"similar projects\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"the MNOC\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"only three months\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniform\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite time being their biggest enemy, the designer duo was able to create a beautiful dress, a masterclass in simple yet majestic fashion that would go down in the annals of Olympic history.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"their biggest enemy\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"the designer duo\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"a beautiful dress\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"a masterclass\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"simple yet majestic fashion\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"the annals\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Table of Contents Mongolia might not be a sporting powerhouse but the country boasts a rich history and culture.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Table\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"Contents Mongolia\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting powerhouse\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"a rich history\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of looking outside for inspiration, the designers drew their inspiration from theNaadam Festival,which is considered their Olympics andtakes place in July every year.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"the designers\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"their inspiration\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"theNaadam Festival\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympics andtakes place\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During this festival, people compete in various competitions wearing similar outfits.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this festival\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"various competitions\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"similar outfits\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic uniform is inspired by Mongolian deels which have been parts of their part of their culture for centuries.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7600760621670413, \"rank\": 0.3151745826382451, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic uniform\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"parts\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"their part\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"their culture\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"centuries\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The designers have added some modern design elements to make their national athletes stand out from the rest.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The designers\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"some modern design elements\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"their national athletes\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of complicating things, the designers chose a simple yet powerful design.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"the designers\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"a simple yet powerful design\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniforms are sharp, and precise, with boxy vests and embroidered collars.\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The uniforms\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"boxy vests\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"embroidered collars\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This design pattern avoids overcomplication, resulting in a timeless elegance that appeals to both classic and modern sensibilities.\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This design pattern\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"overcomplication\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"a timeless elegance\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2794}, {\"ngram\": \"both classic and modern sensibilities\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniform is a perfect amalgamation of simplicity and modernity.\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The uniform\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect amalgamation\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"simplicity\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"modernity\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The designers have paid great attention to detail, especially in the embroidery.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The designers\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"great attention\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"detail\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"the embroidery\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They deliberately designed every aspect of the costume to communicate symbolism.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every aspect\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"the costume\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"symbolism\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every little needlework has a deep underlying meaning.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every little needlework\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"a deep underlying meaning\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 'Nine White Banner' represents fresh starts, while the mountains reflect the athletes' journey and hard work.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 'Nine White Banner\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh starts\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"the mountains\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' journey\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The use of golden thread in the embroidery signifies their desire to win gold medals.\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The use\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"golden thread\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"the embroidery\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"their desire\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This meticulous integration of symbols adds meaning to the design, transforming the uniforms into a story about the Mongolian spirit and ambition.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3452, \"end\": 3461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.7600760621670413, \"rank\": 0.3151745826382451, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This meticulous integration\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3363}, {\"ngram\": \"symbols\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3374}, {\"ngram\": \"meaning\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniforms\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"ambition\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These intricate details offer a touch of refinement without dominating the design.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These intricate details\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"a touch\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"refinement\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3534}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At a time when flashy colours have become the norm, the designers made the practical needs of their athletes their topmost priority.\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3578}, {\"ngram\": \"flashy colours\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3598}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3619}, {\"ngram\": \"the designers\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"the practical needs\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"their athletes\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of choosing extravagant colours, they picked light colours like white and grey, making the fabric more breathable inhot weather in Paris.\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3841, \"end\": 3846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1383024715097073e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extravagant colours\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3741}, {\"ngram\": \"light colours\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3768}, {\"ngram\": \"the fabric\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from being cool (pun intended) the choice of colours conveys a sense of tranquillity and sophistication.\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the choice\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3896}, {\"ngram\": \"colours\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3907}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"tranquillity\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"sophistication\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, the fabrics used are lightweight and comfortable, making sure that the athletes move freely without any discomfort throughout the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4113, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fabrics\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"any discomfort\", \"from\": 4066, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Specialty:Journalism Qualification:PG Diploma Journalismfrom IIMC Experience:6Years\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4177, \"end\": 4181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IIMC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Specialty\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4124}, {\"ngram\": \"Journalism Qualification\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4149}]}]}"